snippet.title: Polly The Frog 2: Island Hopper (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Download: https://brad-games.itch.io/polly-the-frog-2



Polly The Frog 2: Island Hopper is coming out on March 23rd, 2021! With the ability to eat enemies and charge his jump to jump super high, Polly is more equipped than ever in this sequel! Help Polly escape this tropical island!
